--- !u!114 &1582986069
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1582986067}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9f505bb075469dd4eb70fc72ee1e0370, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ObjecteLectura
  text: "Aqu\xED viu Orlan, un home solitari que sempre treballa al taller de fusta.
    No parla gaire, per\xF2 quan passa, ens ofereix consells sobre com cuidar les
    eines o reparar mobles. Ara la casa est\xE0 quieta; potser ha sortit a buscar
    fusta al bosc."
